HELP THERMOMETER                                        Steve Knight, 4/2/94
                                                        SIREN Project

lib thermometer

new_thermometer( LABEL ) -> THERMOMETER
thermometer_label( THERMOMETER ) -> LABEL
LABEL -> thermometer_label( THERMOMETER )
thermometer_level( THERMOMETER ) -> NUMBER
NUMBER -> thermometer_level( THERMOMETER )
show_thermometer( THERMOMETER )
hide_thermometer( THERMOMETER )

This library makes available a simple package for displaying a
graphical "wait thermometer".  You can set the label and level of
the thermometer interactively.
